==旅游==
奥斯穆斯岛作为旅游地点于2002年开始被人注意，当年由2000游客访问。<ref name=kkk>{{Cite web |title=Osmussaare maastikukaitseala kaitsekorralduskava 2004-2008 (Protection plan of Osmussaar Landscape Reserve 2004-2008) |url=http://www.osmussaar.ee/est/?download=Osmussaare_kkk_loplik_30112004.pdf |language=爱沙尼亚语 |year=2003 |accessdate=4 June 2009 |archive-date=2019-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101153401/https://www.osmussaar.ee/est/?download=Osmussaare_kkk_loplik_30112004.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>自后每年夏季都有3000余人访问该岛。<ref name=pm>{{Cite news |first=Andrus |last=Karnau |title=Osmussaarlaste järglased tahavad talumaid tagasi |work=[[Postimees|Postimees]] |date=12 January 2006 |accessdate=4 June 2009 |language=爱沙尼亚语 |url=http://www.postimees.ee/130106/esileht/siseuudised/188565.php |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120526040812/http://www.postimees.ee/130106/esileht/siseuudised/188565.php |archivedate=2012年5月26日 }}</ref>

